        "subtitle": "Figured Sycamore Meets Premium Damascus",
        "intro_content": "<p>The <strong>Hezhen B30 Master Series</strong> combines a <strong>10Cr15CoMoV steel core</strong> clad in 67 layers of Damascus steel with striking <strong>figured sycamore wood handles</strong> — a distinctive pairing that sets it apart from every other series in the range. At <strong>60 HRC</strong>, the 10Cr15CoMoV core delivers the same proven edge retention, corrosion resistance, and toughness found across Xinzuo’s premium lineup, refined through vacuum heat treatment and deep freezing. With 11 knife types from paring to a 10-inch carving knife, plus a bone chopper, cleaver, and nakiri, the Master Series handles everything from delicate prep to heavy-duty tasks. The unique grain of each sycamore handle means no two knives are identical. Part of the Hezhen sub-brand, the Master Series is ideal for Australian cooks who appreciate handcrafted character and want a complete, cohesive knife collection with genuine personality.</p>",
